    "# L3 M9.2: Financial Compliance Risk - Risk Assessment in Retrieval\n",
    "\n",
    "## Learning Arc\n",
    "\n",
    "**Purpose:** Build production-ready risk assessment and compliance guardrails for financial RAG systems to prevent unauthorized investment advice and ensure regulatory compliance.\n",
    "\n",
    "**Concepts Covered:**\n",
    "- Query risk classification using pattern matching and semantic analysis\n",
    "- Multi-factor confidence scoring (retrieval quality, source diversity, temporal consistency, citation agreement)\n",
    "- Regulatory compliance guardrails (RIA, MNPI, Safe Harbor, Form 8-K)\n",
    "- Human-in-the-loop escalation workflows for high-risk queries\n",
    "- User context adjustment for account type and query history\n",
    "- Adversarial query handling and edge case management\n",
    "\n",
    "**After Completing This Notebook:**\n",
    "- You will understand the legal distinction between financial information and investment advice\n",
    "- You can implement hybrid risk classification (pattern + semantic)\n",
    "- You will recognize when queries require RIA escalation\n",
    "- You can build multi-factor confidence scoring systems\n",
    "- You will understand SEC regulations (RIA Act 1940, Reg FD, Safe Harbor, 8-K)\n",
    "- You can design compliance audit trails for financial RAG systems\n",
    "\n",
    "**Context in Track L3.M9:**\n",
    "This module builds on L3 M7 (Financial Document Types) and L3 M8 (Metadata Structures) and prepares you for L3 M10 (Multi-Document Synthesis with Citation).\n",
    "\n",
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## The Case Study\n",
    "\n",
    "**February 2023:** A well-funded fintech startup with a beautiful AI-powered investment platform got hit with a **$12 million SEC fine**.\n",
    "\n",
    "The issue? Their RAG system crossed from providing information into providing investment advice without RIA (Registered Investment Advisor) licensing.\n",
    "\n",
    "**Critical Legal Distinction:**\n",
    "- âœ… **Legal (Information):** \"Tesla's P/E ratio is 65\"\n",
    "- ❌ **Investment Advice (requires RIA):** \"Tesla's P/E is high, consider waiting\"\n",
    "\n",
    "SEC enforcement is **behavior-based**, not intent-based. Disclaimers don't protect you if your system behaves like an advisor."
   ]
