    "## 4. Multi-Factor Confidence Scoring\n",
    "\n",
    "Confidence scoring combines **5 factors**:\n",
    "1. **Retrieval Quality (40%):** Average semantic similarity of top 5 docs\n",
    "2. **Source Diversity (25%):** Number of unique source types (10-K, 8-K, earnings call, etc.)\n",
    "3. **Temporal Consistency (20%):** Fraction of sources from same fiscal period\n",
    "4. **Citation Agreement (15%):** Degree sources align on numerical claims\n",
    "5. **Domain Relevance (bonus):** Financial keywords in query (+0.05 max)\n",
    "\n",
    "### Thresholds:\n",
    "- **≥0.85 (HIGH):** Answer with standard disclaimer\n",
    "- **0.70-0.84 (MEDIUM):** Answer with \"moderate confidence\" warning\n",
    "- **0.50-0.69 (LOW):** Warn \"information may be incomplete\"\n",
    "- **<0.50 (VERY_LOW):** Refuse to answer, escalate"
   ]
